58
00:06:27,747 --> 00:06:30,738
Sunflowers symbolize sunshine and health.

59
00:06:30,738 --> 00:06:35,121
Mr. Sheng, Mr. Hua said he'd like to visit you.

60
00:06:35,121 --> 00:06:37,590
