92
00:08:32,304 --> 00:08:33,906
Hope you have a child soon.

93
00:08:33,906 --> 00:08:35,975
May you always be of one heart and mind,

94
00:08:35,975 --> 00:08:37,909
and grow old together lovingly.

95
00:08:49,255 --> 00:08:50,889
