97
00:08:53,192 --> 00:08:54,593
I haven't seen you in so long.

98
00:08:54,593 --> 00:08:57,096
Don't you want to see me?

99
00:08:57,096 --> 00:08:59,265
We video chat every day.

100
00:08:59,265 --> 00:09:01,233
I have pheromone disorder.

101
00:09:01,233 --> 00:09:04,569
