102
00:09:05,604 --> 00:09:07,973
I made fish soup for you.

103
00:09:07,973 --> 00:09:09,908
Would you like to try some?

104
00:09:11,610 --> 00:09:13,211
Okay.

105
00:09:46,879 --> 00:09:48,047
You shouldn't have come.

106
00:09:48,047 --> 00:09:49,148
