142
00:11:51,403 --> 00:11:53,439
I'll change your inhibitor patch.

143
00:11:53,439 --> 00:11:55,039
Okay.

144
00:12:05,250 --> 00:12:07,119
Mr. Sheng, done with work?

145
00:12:07,119 --> 00:12:08,954
Yes, I just finished.

146
00:12:08,954 --> 00:12:10,089
What are you doing?

147
00:12:10,089 --> 00:12:11,890
I'm watching TV.

148
00:12:11,890 --> 00:12:13,092
What's on?

149
00:12:13,092 --> 00:12:17,029
Watching you in the forum.

150
00:12:17,029 --> 00:12:19,164
You looked so handsome.

151
00:12:19,164 --> 00:12:22,801
Where are you going next?

152
00:12:22,801 --> 00:12:24,370
To see someone I hate.

153
00:12:24,370 --> 00:12:25,970
Huh?

154
00:12:26,772 --> 00:12:30,009
Anyone hated by you is so unlucky.

155
00:12:30,009 --> 00:12:31,443
Why say that?

156
00:12:31,443 --> 00:12:35,147
You're so great, everyone wants your favor.

157
00:12:35,147 --> 00:12:38,850
So, being hated by you must suck.

158
00:12:41,754 --> 00:12:43,288
My mung bean soup is boiling over.

159
00:12:43,288 --> 00:12:46,125
Gotta go. You can have some when you're back.

160
00:12:46,125 --> 00:12:47,725
Bye.

161
00:12:55,801 --> 00:12:57,336
Leave.

162
00:12:57,336 --> 00:13:01,507
Can't be late
for my first afternoon tea with Mr. Sheng.

163
00:13:01,507 --> 00:13:03,107
Yes, sir.

164
00:13:05,411 --> 00:13:09,281
Such a fuss,
with inspectors as patrol officers.

165
00:13:09,281 --> 00:13:13,318
Is the guy from X Holdings
some overlord from Country P?

166
00:13:14,753 --> 00:13:16,387
Mr. Sheng.

167
00:13:17,056 --> 00:13:19,191
Hope you've been well.

168
00:13:19,191 --> 00:13:20,726
Thanks to your master's hospitality,

169
00:13:20,726 --> 00:13:22,494
it's my first afternoon tea here

170
00:13:22,494 --> 00:13:25,397
