and commissioners directing traffic.

171
00:13:25,397 --> 00:13:27,633
Even a small country president's private visit

172
00:13:27,633 --> 00:13:30,803
wouldn't have this much fanfare.

173
00:13:30,803 --> 00:13:32,104
You flatter us.

174
00:13:32,104 --> 00:13:35,306
We owe it all to your city's kindness.
This way, please.

175
00:13:38,911 --> 00:13:41,413
Have you thought about how this will end?

176
00:13:41,413 --> 00:13:42,714
I have.

177
00:13:42,714 --> 00:13:44,016
I love him.

178
00:13:44,016 --> 00:13:46,285
I could play an Omega beside him forever.

179
00:13:46,285 --> 00:13:48,954
What if he wants to permanently mark you?

180
00:13:48,954 --> 00:13:50,956
I'll remove my gland,

181
00:13:50,956 --> 00:13:54,359
say it was injured and I became a Beta.

182
00:13:54,359 --> 00:13:56,428
