183
00:13:56,428 --> 00:13:58,030
You think it's tonsillectomy?

184
00:13:58,030 --> 00:13:59,832
Accidental pheromone gland injury

185
00:13:59,832 --> 00:14:01,066
has a zero-percent survival rate.

186
00:14:01,066 --> 00:14:04,737
My body functions better than S-class Alphas.

187
00:14:04,737 --> 00:14:07,772
