201
00:14:58,157 --> 00:15:01,226
Sir, Mr. Sheng from Sheng Fang Biotech is here.

202
00:15:01,226 --> 00:15:06,030
Chang Yu, bring a chair for Mr. Sheng's team.

203
00:15:25,918 --> 00:15:28,486
Secretary Chen, please sit.

204
00:15:33,759 --> 00:15:36,094
