209
00:15:57,216 --> 00:15:58,917
What are you saying, Mr. Sheng?

210
00:15:58,917 --> 00:16:03,589
X Holdings had an industry exchange conference.

211
00:16:03,589 --> 00:16:08,026
Sheng Fang's absence was a real pity.

212
00:16:08,026 --> 00:16:15,200
We've invited you today
to build basic mutual understanding.

213
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:18,904
X Holdings is a global industry leader.

214
00:16:18,904 --> 00:16:23,307
It's our honor that you wish
to learn about Sheng Fang.

215
00:16:25,911 --> 00:16:27,346
Pin Ming.

216
00:16:27,346 --> 00:16:28,813
