261
00:19:37,836 --> 00:19:38,837
Yes.

262
00:19:38,837 --> 00:19:41,606
Sir, please trust us.
Mr. Sheng didn't do it on purpose.

263
00:19:41,606 --> 00:19:43,508
- He…
- What if he did?

264
00:19:43,508 --> 00:19:45,343
