I understand.

542
00:39:44,408 --> 00:39:46,176
A pharmaceutical friend said this.

543
00:39:46,176 --> 00:39:49,246
X Holdings' targeted drug
has completed formulation

544
00:39:49,246 --> 00:39:50,981
with excellent results.

545
00:39:50,981 --> 00:39:52,650
If we can contact the person in charge

546
00:39:52,650 --> 00:39:54,451
to get the drug early,

547
00:39:54,451 --> 00:39:58,455
it would help the chairman significantly.

548
00:40:11,435 --> 00:40:13,871
I went grocery shopping for dinner.

549
00:40:13,871 --> 00:40:16,073
If you want something special,

550
00:40:16,073 --> 00:40:18,575
text me when you see this note.

551
00:40:18,575 --> 00:40:21,444
I'll pick it up on the way. Hua Yong.

552
00:40:30,921 --> 00:40:32,356
Hello, Mr. Sheng.

553
00:40:32,356 --> 00:40:33,724
Are you done?

554
00:40:33,724 --> 00:40:36,092
Yes. I just got home

555
00:40:37,594 --> 00:40:39,697
I've bought the groceries
and will be back soon.

556
00:40:39,697 --> 00:40:42,800
Anything specific you want me to buy?

557
00:40:42,800 --> 00:40:44,468
No.

558
00:40:44,468 --> 00:40:47,171
Shall I send a driver to pick you up?

559
00:40:47,171 --> 00:40:50,039
No, the subway is convenient.

560
00:40:53,010 --> 00:40:57,681
Why leave a note instead of messaging directly?

561
00:40:57,681 --> 00:40:59,249
I wasn't sure if you were busy

562
00:40:59,249 --> 00:41:01,217
and didn't want to disturb you.

563
00:41:01,919 --> 00:41:03,754
Mr. Sheng, it's my turn to pay.

564
00:41:03,754 --> 00:41:06,122
I'll hang up. See you soon.

565
00:41:06,924 --> 00:41:08,359
Okay.

566
00:41:08,359 --> 00:41:09,959
See you.

567
00:41:21,572 --> 00:41:23,073
Without a targeted drug,

568
00:41:23,073 --> 00:41:24,508
once the tumor spreads,

569
00:41:24,508 --> 00:41:26,343
it will reach severe stages.

570
00:41:26,343 --> 00:41:31,748
Even with a drug then, it may be too late.

571
00:41:44,667 --> 00:41:53,834
[Chang Yu]

572
00:41:55,038 --> 00:41:57,274
Mr. Sheng, I just finished shopping

573
00:41:57,274 --> 00:41:59,909
and will be back soon.

574
00:42:03,080 --> 00:42:07,217
Mr. Sheng, I'm on the subway
and will be home shortly.

575
00:42:17,761 --> 00:42:21,031
Boss, Mr. Sheng called.

576
00:42:21,031 --> 00:42:23,133
Should we call back soon?

577
00:42:23,133 --> 00:42:24,568
No.

578
00:42:24,568 --> 00:42:27,638
He's probably asking about the targeted drug.

579
00:42:27,638 --> 00:42:29,473
Call back in two hours.

580
00:42:29,473 --> 00:42:30,840
Understood.

581
00:42:33,444 --> 00:42:36,647
The drug formulation just finished.

582
00:42:36,647 --> 00:42:38,115
The maximum dosage test for human application

583
00:42:38,115 --> 00:42:42,453
can start earliest on the day after tomorrow.

584
00:42:42,453 --> 00:42:44,053
Got it.

585
00:42:44,955 --> 00:42:47,691
I've already hinted to Wen Lang.

586
00:42:47,691 --> 00:42:51,495
Tell Mr. Sheng that
the drug's person in charge will contact him.

587
00:42:51,495 --> 00:42:52,929
Yes.

588
00:42:54,164 --> 00:42:57,568
Boss, you oversaw this personally.

589
00:42:57,568 --> 00:43:01,004
The research teams worldwide
rushed the progress

590
00:43:01,004 --> 00:43:04,441
to expedite it for Mr. Sheng's father.

591
00:43:04,441 --> 00:43:10,214
Wouldn't it be a pity
if he doesn't know your intentions?

592
00:43:10,214 --> 00:43:12,482
It doesn't matter if he knows.

593
00:43:13,317 --> 00:43:18,521
I never wanted his gratitude,
so there's nothing worth regretting.

594
00:43:48,318 --> 00:43:50,120
I forgot my book in the bedroom.

595
00:43:50,120 --> 00:43:51,754
I'm going to get it.

596
00:44:04,467 --> 00:44:06,133
[Chang Yu]

597
00:44:21,385 --> 00:44:23,455
Hello, Secretary Chang.

598
00:44:23,455 --> 00:44:25,022
Mr. Sheng.

599
00:44:25,022 --> 00:44:27,324
Why the sudden call?

600
00:44:27,324 --> 00:44:30,727
I need your advice on something.

601
00:44:30,727 --> 00:44:32,929
Is it convenient to talk now?

602
00:44:34,464 --> 00:44:36,599
Go ahead.

603
00:44:37,267 --> 00:44:41,505
I heard X Holdings'
targeted pheromone gland cancer drug

604
00:44:41,505 --> 00:44:43,574
has completed formulation.

605
00:44:43,574 --> 00:44:45,609
News travels fast.

606
00:44:45,609 --> 00:44:46,910
Yes.

607
00:44:46,910 --> 00:44:50,013
Our drug is indeed near clinical trials.

608
00:44:50,013 --> 00:44:53,015
Why the sudden interest?

609
00:44:55,953 --> 00:44:57,787
To be frank,

610
00:44:58,488 --> 00:45:00,990
my father needs this drug.

611
00:45:01,992 --> 00:45:05,796
You mean Sheng Fang's chairman?

612
00:45:05,796 --> 00:45:07,931
Yes.

613
00:45:07,931 --> 00:45:10,433
He's been on medical leave.

614
00:45:11,234 --> 00:45:13,270
It's pheromone gland cancer.

615
00:45:13,270 --> 00:45:18,008
Secretary Chang, I know your formula
is still confidential.

616
00:45:18,008 --> 00:45:22,479
But I'm not calling as a biopharm CEO today.

617
00:45:22,479 --> 00:45:27,049
I'm calling as a son
begging for help for my father.

618
00:45:31,888 --> 00:45:33,856
Please help me.

